[[unpartei/CopyClip|CopyClip]][[http://google.com/search?q=CopyClip| ° ]] is a breakthroug annotation technique, where the clip retains full functionality of all links.
The free webservice [[unpartei/ClipBoardPlus|ClipBoardPlus]][[http://google.com/search?q=ClipBoardPlus| ° ]] makes this possible.

